---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Bindery & Finishing — Frye's Printing" description="Complete bindery and finishing services in Napa Valley. Cutting, folding, binding, laminating, and specialty finishing.">
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/services" class="text-gold text-sm font-medium hover:text-gold-light transition-colors">&larr; All Services</a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-4">Bindery &amp; Finishing</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-lg mt-4 max-w-2xl">
        The final touches make all the difference. Our in-house bindery and finishing capabilities ensure your printed piece is delivered ready to use.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">The Perfect Finish</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Printing is only half the story. The way a piece is cut, folded, bound, and finished determines how it feels in someone's hands — and that tactile experience matters. Our in-house bindery team handles every finishing detail with precision and care.
              </p>
              <p>
                Because our finishing equipment is right here alongside our presses, we maintain complete control over quality and timing throughout the entire production process. No waiting on outside vendors, no surprises.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Our Capabilities</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              {['Cutting & Trimming', 'Folding & Scoring', 'Saddle Stitching', 'Perfect Binding', 'Wire-O & Spiral Binding', 'Padding', 'Drilling & Punching', 'Collating & Assembly', 'Laminating', 'UV Coating', 'Numbering & Perforating', 'Die Cutting'].map((item) => (
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-charcoal-light">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  {item}
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Why Finishing at Frye's?</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                <strong class="text-navy">All under one roof.</strong> No outsourcing delays. Your job goes from press to bindery without leaving the building.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-navy">Attention to detail.</strong> Our bindery team takes pride in clean cuts, precise folds, and tight registration. The small things add up to a noticeably better finished product.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-warm-gray rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-28">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-4">Get a Quote</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-light text-sm mb-5">
              Need special finishing on your print project? We can help.
            </p>
            <a href="/quote" class="block w-full px-6 py-3 bg-terracotta text-white text-center font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-terracotta-light transition-colors">
              Request a Quote
            </a>
            <p class="text-charcoal-light text-xs mt-4 text-center">
              Or call <a href="tel:707-253-1114" class="text-terracotta hover:text-terracotta-light">(707) 253-1114</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
